description: LithiumBank Resources Corp., an exploration and development company, focuses on lithium-brine properties in Canada. Its properties portfolio includes Boardwalk, Swan Hills, Kakwa, Valhalla, Fox Creek, Simonette, Nipisi, Peace, Estevan, Kindersley, South, and Valleyview in Alberta and Saskatchewan. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
